# Title: Suspicious Calculator Usage
# Author: Florian Roth (Nextron Systems)
# Date: 2019-02-09
# Level: high
# Description: Detects suspicious use of 'calc.exe' with command line parameters or in a suspicious directory, which is likely caused by some PoC or detection evasion.
# MITRE Tactic: Uncategorized
# Tags: attack.stealth, attack.t1036
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/process_creation/proc_creation_win_calc_uncommon_exec.yml

CommandLine="*\\calc.exe *" OR (Image="*\\calc.exe" NOT (Image IN ("*:\\Windows\\System32\\*", "*:\\Windows\\SysWOW64\\*", "*:\\Windows\\WinSxS\\*")))